name: Untitled Frog Boss
description:
There's a frog boss and it wants you to fall down a trapdoor.
(You don't want to fall down a trapdoor)

To move:
Press the arrow keys if you're right-handed
Alternatively press WASD if you're right-handed and want to bend your elbow in a mildly uncomfortable way.
